{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 131959, "create_time": 1653154529, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "清零政策个人感觉需要掌握一个度。目前看来应该是在度内的。换句话说，即便是现在清零不正确吧。恐怕，如此大规模清零也是有史以来第一次吧，这会积累很多经验，为人类未来预防更大的类似传染病的灾难打好宝贵的基础。", "timestamp": 1653154529}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 131978, "create_time": 1653155000, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "自我奉献的精神，为全人类谋福利", "timestamp": 1653155000}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 131982, "create_time": 1653155070, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "清零是一天实现的吗", "timestamp": 1653155070}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 132018, "create_time": 1653156460, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "至少目前足够严格的措施是可以清零的。\n只是在清零到自己头上之前，我都是觉得清零是好的，因为我受益。", "timestamp": 1653156460}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 132051, "create_time": 1653157977, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 这个度由谁来裁定呢？其他人为什么要牺牲生计、健康和自由，为这场不知道结果的实验做小白鼠呢？你们喜欢宏大叙事，言必大谋略，口口声声为了「人民」乃至「人类」，什么时候能为「人」着想一下呢。", "timestamp": 1653157977}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 132052, "create_time": 1653158014, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 请问中国人就不是人吗？", "timestamp": 1653158014}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 132053, "create_time": 1653158047, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 不知道是不是一天实现，只看到是一天世界。", "timestamp": 1653158047}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": 